#                                                                                                                                                                                                       

[media]

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

[media]

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

[media]

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

[media]

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

[media]

**Christmas Update**
- New Xmas Battlepass
- Christmas Ornament Hunt
- New Rudolf Bundle
- Christmas Themed Levels

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/499303746_2181339939044468_540727540857874572_n.mp4?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=DUH9irxyFOcQ7kNvwHmdZex&_nc_oc=AdkPQM-HMXfMyR899lCKgsjaVQijOOM5dkN4tNkaa3k7tgBmiKKZJTqjGB8wqugLR7M&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=dckl_rlvdouoa3ihN6dGfA&oh=00_AfrFhvMklRiWk92waWoqkA-J3Y8LoXDAHyc5MF0xgd5pUA&oe=696AABA4)

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/491830888_1234204841304584_7133986973260987280_n.mp4?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=JHe2U7WSlYoQ7kNvwFTzSC-&_nc_oc=AdmJkQhNavi5QZRDQiJOs3wketaSingI3tI5Y8Oznl0U3LvOmcUEPivtK-qnHgesg-8&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=dckl_rlvdouoa3ihN6dGfA&oh=00_AfqxuHqP_1iVWOXtzwwle-BMGsAvzK7nHquV0HbLM45d3w&oe=696A79BC)

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/491821117_1430846481437060_8099142216261706884_n.mp4?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=95gsZ-Vb_kQQ7kNvwFsd_Vv&_nc_oc=AdkzOymkGkDOWueR79C6VfweRoS7Y6UunItAX3cocsP7ukXOfRJ1gA0OtYCKeZe9vQY&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=dckl_rlvdouoa3ihN6dGfA&oh=00_Afoy_IzAe9YuU0KLsqe_cOavdQe6CSIKZ8dM6MIuzTyThQ&oe=696AA0CC)

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

![{"height":1440,"type":"image","width":2560}](https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/499292426_757548860702625_520424425045914625_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=uxs6IrX7Hy0Q7kNvwG8bLmz&_nc_oc=AdmbadJyxTBZGg1j3f8z_aD1PaEOwlPpcBz5oS1wurgeKIyPPI6ZrGpwdUgenjteMFo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AfprEiRbmGUDSGsoZgGgG5_wh6lMUxx9OOXQejB5wDyEUQ&oe=696A9E32)
